name: Cosmochoria
blurb: A tiny, naked cosmonaut with a jetpack & laser blaster must revive a dying galaxy by planting one seed at a time. (Mac/PC/Linux/Wii U)

rewards.reward:
THE 'SEEDLING' TIER 
============================= 
For $3, you can show your support in making this game (and my dream) a reality. Plus, you'll get some hi-res backer-only wallpapers & icons for your computer to show how cool you are to all your classmates and co-workers.  
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ 
Also, donating to this tier—or any other tier—means I will ensure 1 tree gets safely planted for you on this Earth.

THE 'EARLY BIRD' TIER 
============================= 
Limited to the first 1000 backers, for $9, you get a DRM-Free digital copy of Cosmochoria when it's released. You'll also receive a digital copy of the Soundtrack Preview EP "Seeds", featuring music by Ilkae and Zebra as well as the PDF Instruction Manual, backer wallpapers and icons.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ 
Also, there is that additional bonus of a tree being planted just for you!

THE 'GAME TIME' TIER 
============================= 
For $12, you get a DRM-Free digital copy of Cosmochoria when it's released. You'll also receive the digital copy of the "Seeds" EP, featuring music by Ilkae and Zebra as well as the PDF Instruction Manual, backer wallpapers and icons.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ 
Let's not forget about that tree that will be planted. That's included.

THE 'YOGSNAUGHT' TIER 
============================= 
For $15, you get a DRM-Free digital copy of Cosmochoria when it's released, but with a special unlock code to play as the one and only Yogscast's Simon. 
============================= 
You'll also receive the digital copy of the "Seeds" EP, featuring music by Ilkae and Zebra as well as the PDF Instruction Manual, backer wallpapers and icons.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ 
Let's not forget about that tree that will be planted. That's included.

THE 'DEV TEAM' TIER 
============================= 
For $25, you will receive a DRM-Free digital copy of Cosmochoria; the PDF Instruction Manual; a free digital copy of the "Seeds" EP as well as early access to the final game—giving you not only a chance to play Cosmochoria before anyone else, but also influence the final stages of development of the game with your direct input!
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ 
You're probably thinking: "Man this tier sure would be killer if he also included a tree planted somewhere on this sweet mama  planet of ours." Well guess what? Boom. Done. Planted.

THE 'CARTOON ME' TIER ============================= 
For $40, I will draw a customized Cosmonaut for you in the same style as the game's artwork. I'll provide you the high resolution artwork ready for printing or any other purpose you desire as you have full rights to use it for whatever you like (company logo, twitter avatar, etc). The character will look similar to the style I used for Cosmo and Simon, but with features personalized for YOU!
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
This tier also includes a digital copy of Cosmochoria + the "Seeds" EP.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ 
You'll also get that Tree.

THE 'NOT NAKED' TIER ============================= 
For $60, you'll receive a limited edition high quality T-Shirt with art exclusive to this Kickstarter campaign. I will contact you for your size once the campaign is complete. Shipping to Canada & US is included, hence the price jump from the last tier. T-Shirt art will be revealed on April 7th!
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ 
This tier also includes the DRM-Free digital copies of Cosmochoria + The "Seeds" EP as well as the PDF instruction manual, wallpapers and icons.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ 
Don't forget about the tree. The tree that will be planted if you pledge!

THE 'ART BUFF' TIER ============================= 
For $85, you'll receive an ultra-limited edition, high quality, signed & numbered (#51-100) canvas art print. This tier also includes the DRM-Free digital copies of Cosmochoria + The "Seeds" EP as well as the PDF instruction manual, wallpapers and icons.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ 
Look, someone's getting hit in the boingloings. Boingloings. Boingloings. Just kidding. Tree.

THE 'COLLECTOR' TIER ============================= 
For $100 you will receive a limited edition, Kickstarter-only physical version of Cosmochoria. This package includes hand sewn felt "Tentacle" pouch and a one-of-a-kind laser-engraved Wooden USB loaded with the DRM-Free versions of Cosmochoria and the "Seeds" EP. Other digital goodies like timelapse videos of artwork in progress, sketches and scans of my notes and work surrounding the development of Cosmochoria and other digital surprises. This version also includes a physically printed version of the instruction manual.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ 
And the tree.

THE 'SUPER FAN' TIER ============================= 
For $200 you receive ALL physical items, including a signed and numbered (#6-50) canvas print, the Kickstarter exclusive T-Shirt, the limited edition Collectors USB Edition and you name in the game credits as Super Fan (or something cooler, probably). Plus some additional surprise goodies (stickers, postcards, etc).
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ 
Want more air? Cool, this pledge level also includes the planting of a tree. It will make air for you.

THE 'ONE-OF-5' TIER ============================= 
This tier comes with ALL rewards listed above: 1 copy of Cosmochoria; 1 Seeds EP; 1 T-Shirt; 1 Signed & Numbered Canvas Print (#1-5); 1 Signed & Numbered Collectors USB Edition & Printed Manual (#1-5); 1 Planted Tree.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
PLUS an ultra-rare, super limited edition, signed & numbered (#1-5), hand-crafted 10inch ’Cosmo’ Plush Toy with detachable plush jetpack.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
This tier is no joke, and for that reason I have decided to not include a joke about the tree.

THE 'WORLD CREATOR' TIER ============================= 
For $350 you will receive the ability to directly influence the appearance of your very own planet in the galaxy of Cosmochoria. I will work with you personally to illustrate a Planet in a style of your choosing. The illustration may include likenesses of loved ones or pets, or just an abstract representation of your own beautiful existence. The planet will appear randomly in every game of Cosmochoria.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ 
Some Rules: The Planet illustration cannot be blatantly promotional to a company or brand, but I will work with you closely to incorporate something that means something special to you, or even a representation of a character, loved one or another visual metaphor.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ 
You will not only receive your planet in-game, but I will produce a high quality, signed, one-of-a-kind 8x10 canvas print of your planet and ship it to you, as well as provide the hi-resolution source art printable at additional sizes. Your name will also appear in the credits (with accompanying URL if you like) for your contribution. 
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ 
This tier also includes a DRM-Free digital copy of Cosmochoria + the "Seeds" EP, plus early access to the game. 
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ 
This tier does not include a tree planted in your honour. It includes 3 trees planted for you in your honour.

THE 'NARCISSISM RUNS DEEP' TIER ============================= 
For $400 you will work directly with me to create your illustrated likeness to appear in Cosmochoria as a secret unlockable & fully playable character. Your character can also have a simple super power (within reason and my coding abilities). Your name will be listed in the credits for your contribution.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ 
(Optional) You will not only receive your character in-game, but I will produce a high quality, signed, one-of-a-kind 8x10 canvas print of the illustration and ship it to you, as well as provide the hi-resolution source art printable at additional sizes. 
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ 
This tier also includes a DRM-Free digital copy of Cosmochoria + the "Seeds" EP, plus early access to the game. 
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ 
Instead of a tree, I'll plant your human DNA in the soil and nurture it until a baby you comes out of the ground. Then I'll raise the baby you into adulthood and force it to plant raspberry bushes all over your yard. Then I'll wait until they produce berries and pick them all while you sleep soundly in your bed. I'll feed the grown up baby you berries until it can eat no more and then take it to the park to play. You did this. Actually, nevermind. Tree.

THE 'POWERFUL DEATHLORD OF SPACE' TIER ============================= 
For $500 you will work directly with me to create an evil enemy that will appear in Cosmochoria. Your name will be listed (with accompanying URL if you like) in the credits for your contribution.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ 
You will not only receive your enemy in-game, but I will produce a high quality, signed, one-of-a-kind 8x10 canvas print of your enemy and ship it to you, as well as provide the hi-resolution source art printable at additional sizes. 
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ 
This tier also includes a DRM-Free digital copy of Cosmochoria + the "Seeds" EP, plus early access to the game. 
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ 
Honestly, this tier doesn't include a tree planted - in fact, If you pledge this tier I'll personally go into the forest by my house and snap a branch of an already fully grown tree. Then i'll feel bad about it and make sure Earth Day Network plants a tree to ease my regret. It's not for you this time, though. It's for me.

THE 'CREATIVE COLLABORATOR' TIER ============================= 
For $1000 you will work directly with me to create an element from all 3 of the creator tiers: 1) an evil enemy, 2) your own planet, and 3) a playable character fashioned to your liking. 
Your name will be listed (with accompanying URL if you like) in the credits for your contributions.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ 
You will not only receive your creations in-game, but I will produce a high quality, signed, one-of-a-kind 8x10 canvas print of your enemy, planet and character and ship it to you, as well as provide the hi-resolution source art printable at additional sizes. 
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ 
This tier also includes a DRM-Free digital copy of Cosmochoria + the "Seeds" EP, plus early access to the game. 
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ 
This tier also includes a tree planted, just for you!

THE 'PRETTY CREEPY' TIER ============================= 
Ok. Seriously? No, seriously? Alright, for single-handedly bringing this campaign 20% away from the goal, you can basically BECOME ME for a day. I will personally give you (to keep) my current favourite jeans, my current favourite shirt, and my ALL TIME favorite T-Shirt - the threadbare busted up Super Mario Bros T-Shirt my little bro gave me for my birthday in my 20's that is way too small for me but I keep for sentimental purposes. I will also prepare for you my favourite foods throughout the day (fluffernutters and bacon alllll day), provide an endless stream of gin martinis (with 3 jalepeno stuffed olives each) and teach you how to do every little thing I do on a day to day basis from how make drawings, games and music to the specific way I upload files via FTP and even down to the way I sneeze while holding my lower back so as to minimize the laser-like pains that shoot through my legs due to spending so much goddamn time in a computer chair.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ 
The real reward is that you will go back into your life feeling a fuller and more complete human being knowing that anything you do for the rest of your life from that point onwards is more meaningful and rich because of the 24 hours of depravity you experienced on that 'dark day'. Plus you can help me design a playable / unlockable character for the game, an enemy for the game AND your own planet in the game. I'll even list you in the credits right next to my name.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ 
I will not cover travel expenses, but I can promise you will be treated as well as I have ever experienced in my lifetime.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ 
Also, the tree thing.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ 
PS. this is a joke
PPS. that said, i am actually legally bound to provide these wonders if you actually pledged 8 grand. So... Just sayin.
